### Seed Team Configurations
### This file uses httpyac format for seeding team configurations via REST API
### Run these requests to populate team configurations in CosmosDB

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3978
@apiPath = /api/teamconfiguration

### 1. Create Contact Center AI Team (Weekly Milestones)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamId": "contact-center-ai",
  "teamName": "Contact Center AI",
  "iterationPath": "OneCRM\\FY26\\Q3\\1Wk\\1Wk33",
  "areaPaths": [
    "OneCRM\\AI\\ContactCenter"
  ],
  "slaOverrides": {
    "Task": 3
  }
}

### 2. Create Authentication & Anti-Fraud Team (Monthly Milestones)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamId": "auth-antifraud",
  "teamName": "Authentication & Anti-Fraud",
  "iterationPath": "OneCRM\\FY26\\Q3\\Month\\01 Jan",
  "areaPaths": [
    "OneCRM\\Security\\Auth",
    "OneCRM\\Security\\AntiFraud"
  ],
  "slaOverrides": {
    "Feature": 10
  }
}

### 3. Get All Teams
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}

### 4. Get Specific Team
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/contact-center-ai

### 5. Update Team (Example: Update iteration path)
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/contact-center-ai
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamId": "contact-center-ai",
  "teamName": "Contact Center AI",
  "iterationPath": "OneCRM\\FY26\\Q3\\1Wk\\1Wk34",
  "areaPaths": [
    "OneCRM\\AI\\ContactCenter"
  ],
  "slaOverrides": {
    "Task": 3
  }
}

### 6. Delete Team (Cleanup)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/contact-center-ai
